name: The 6th Int'l Conference on Forestry and Animal Husbandry
content: The 6th Int'l Conference on Forestry and Animal Husbandry (FAH 2019) will be held from March 23 to 25, 2019 in Xi'an, China. This Conference will cover issues on Forestry and Animal Husbandry. The aim of FAH 2019 is to provide a stage for researchers, engineers, academicians as well as industrial professionals from all over the world to present their latest research results and advanced research methods.
